# Observe part 1 : Check the containers (i.e. $ sudo docker ps -a)
# Exercise step 2: Connect to webserver2 (i.e. $ sudo docker exe -i -t webserver2 /bin/bash)
# Exercise step 3: Install ping (i.e. $ apt install iputils-ping)
